OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Frain move southeast across Scotland
OL,7,Fand Northern Ireland overnight. Can be
OL,8,Flocally blustery and heavy later in
OL,9,Fthe night. Elsewhere, dry with clear
OL,10,Fspells and lighter winds, allowing a
OL,11,Frural frost to form in places.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FRain in the north gradually
OL,14,Fclear south through the day. Sunny
OL,15,Fspells following with scattered
OL,16,Fshowers in the north and northwest.
OL,17,FFeeling chilly, especially in the
OL,18,Fbrisk northerly breeze.
